        "timestamp": "2019-01-29 09:30:26.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nOfficial response from LF helpdesk:\n\nDear Krzysztof, \n\nIt looks like Gerrit itself has the configuration needed to accept these dependencies. \nUnfortunately our Jenkins jobs are not prepared to build using those dependencies. \n\nI believe we would need to implement multiple SCMs to allow the jobs to clone more than one repo\nsince the current verification is just cloning one project. \nAlso, we will require to write templates to support this verification. \n\nLet me consult this with my team and see if any other project has implemented this. \n\nFor now, having https://gerrit.onap.org/r/#/c/77477/ merged first will be the best thing to do.",
        "patchset_number": 1
